Customize Lists in Messaging Components with New Settings

This change applies to enhanced WhatsApp and enhanced Apple Messages for Business channels. 

To control how messaging components with clickable options appear in messaging sessions, try new settings on the List Selector format. Two types of messaging components use this format: time selectors and questions with options.

On the Messaging Components page in Setup, create a question with options or time selector messaging component. Add the List Selector format to your component, then customize the properties in the properties pane.

Update properties for Initial Message Configuration, Initial Image Configuration to provide text and image shown when agent/bot sends it to customer. Update Confirmation Message Configuration and Confirmation Image Configuration to show different text and image after customer selects an option.
title: Customizing Messaging Components in Salesforce
